The Adobe Sites Optimizer delivered immediate SEO benefits and provided clear guidance for long-term development improvements. Even used as a guide rather than a direct fulcrum for change, it created measurable value and sharpened our optimization roadmap.We appreciate the opportunity to use Site Optimizer in this context and are optimistic about leveraging it within the AEM Cloud environment, where its full capabilities, including true push-button optimization, can deliver far greater efficiency and return on investment.

Humana Existing SEO Tool Stack: April Friese listed current tools in use, including Lighthouse-based internal tools, Semrush, Screaming Frog, and AHrefs, and emphasized the need to ensure Sites Optimizer adds value before further investment.
